data.description: Beautiful and well-maintained home in the highly sought after Brooks / Northgate School District. This spacious property offers ample room for a growing family or those who love to entertain. The open floor plan and abundant natural light create a warm and inviting atmosphere. This stunning home opens to a two-story foyer with LVP flooring. The front formal dining room contains tons of detail while the front spacious office room features french doors and plenty of natural light. The floorplan flows into a large living room that contains a fireplace and built-in shelves perfect for hosting family gatherings. The open concept leads to the bright kitchen full of top-of-the-line appliances and a large island that is a chef's dream. The main floor includes a guest bedroom, full bathroom, and laundry room. The spacious second floor hosts the primary suite. Step into luxury with the primary suite of this exquisite home. With ample space, a walk-in closet, and a beautifully appointed en-suite bathroom, this retreat is designed for relaxation. Discover the perfect blend of comfort and functionality with three additional bedrooms upstairs along with two bathrooms. Each bedroom offers a cozy and private space, ideal for family members or guests. The well-appointed bathrooms provide convenience and style, catering to the needs of a busy household. The large bonus room presents endless possibilities, whether it's a play area, home office, or entertainment space. Leading back to the main level, unleash the potential of the third car garage, providing ample space for your vehicles, extra storage, a workshop area, or even a home gym. Finally, step into the serene oasis of the closed-in patio/sunroom, where indoor comfort meets outdoor tranquility. This versatile space offers a seamless transition from the interior of the home to the beauty of the outdoors. Whether you're savoring a morning coffee or hosting a gathering with friends, the sunroom provides a peaceful retreat in any season all looking out to the private backyard perfect for dogs to run, kids to play and grilling out with friends! This home has easy access to the interstate providing a quick commute to the Airport and all that Atlanta offers!
